
                   <p style="text-align: center">
                       <b>Title:</b> Sometimes a policy can grant permissions that are dangerous for security or dangerous for continued
operations, such as locking out the root user of the account. The StorageGRID S3 REST API implementation is
less restrictive during policy validation than Amazon, but equally strict during policy evaluation.<br>
                       <b>Bounding box:</b> x1=134, y1=298, x2=1566, y2=1881
                   </p>
